msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 10 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 10 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.186:0.2"
msgid "18. Sādhuvagga "
msgstr "18. Good "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 186. Ācayagāmisutta → ācayagāmīsuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an10.186:0.3"
msgid "186. Ācayagāmisutta "
msgstr "186. Leading to Accumulation "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an10.186:1.1"
msgid "“Ācayagāmiñca vo, bhikkhave, dhammaṃ desessāmi apacayagāmiñca. "
msgstr "“I will teach you the principle that leads to accumulation and that which leads to dispersal. … "

msgctxt "an10.186:1.2"
msgid "Taṃ suṇātha … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an10.186:1.3"
msgid "katamo ca, bhikkhave, ācayagāmī dhammo? "
msgstr "And what is the principle that leads to accumulation? "

msgctxt "an10.186:1.4"
msgid "Pāṇātipāto … pe … "
msgstr "Killing living creatures … "

msgctxt "an10.186:1.5"
msgid "micchādiṭṭhi—"
msgstr "wrong view. "

msgctxt "an10.186:1.6"
msgid "ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, ācayagāmī dhammo. "
msgstr "This is called the principle that leads to accumulation. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.277, sc2
msgctxt "an10.186:2.1"
msgid "Katamo ca, bhikkhave, apacayagāmī dhammo? "
msgstr "And what is the principle that leads to dispersal? "

msgctxt "an10.186:2.2"
msgid "Pāṇātipātā veramaṇī … pe … "
msgstr "Not killing living creatures … "

msgctxt "an10.186:2.3"
msgid "sammādiṭṭhi—"
msgstr "right view. "

msgctxt "an10.186:2.4"
msgid "ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, apacayagāmī dhammo”ti. "
msgstr "This is called the principle that leads to dispersal.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an10.186:2.5"
msgid "Navamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
